{"word":"G5081 - τηλαυγῶς - tēlaugōs - tay-low-goce' - Clearly","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τηλαυγῶς</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">tēlaugōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">tay-low-goce'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Clearly</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"தெளிவாய் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"at a distance and clearly, radiantly, in full light, clearly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from a compound of a derivative of <a href=\"#/G5056 - τέλος - télos - tel'-os/5056\">G5056</a> and <a href=\"#/G827 - αὐγή - augḗ - owg'-ay/827\">G827</a>; in a <i>far shining</i> manner, that is, <i>plainly:</i> - clearly.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}